I... Okay.

543
00:39:21,868 --> 00:39:23,031
I had no choice.

544
00:39:23,142 --> 00:39:26,586
We were both doing that
"are we more than friends" thing, and...

545
00:39:26,677 --> 00:39:27,870
And... I wanted to be,

546
00:39:27,921 --> 00:39:30,650
but I knew that
if I canceled on you again,

547
00:39:30,685 --> 00:39:33,172
then you'd... That I'd lose you, so...

548
00:39:35,750 --> 00:39:37,611
Yeah, you probably would have.

549
00:39:38,611 --> 00:39:39,612
Right.

550
00:39:47,377 --> 00:39:49,490
I can get the cop away
from the building.

551
00:40:19,762 --> 00:40:20,515
What'd you do?

552
00:40:20,550 --> 00:40:22,008
Don't ask. You get the package?

553
00:40:22,049 --> 00:40:23,668
